    <title>How to use icons from Font Awesome 5.x in your website?</title>
    <url>/2021/06/30/How-to-use-Font-Awesome-in-your-website/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="Referencing-Icons"><a href="#Referencing-Icons" class="headerlink" title="Referencing Icons"></a>Referencing Icons</h2><p>First of all, I suspect that the version of embedded Font Awesome to be 5, because New in Font Awesome 5 is the <strong>fas prefix</strong> or <strong>fab prefix</strong>, while Font Awesome 4 uses <strong>fa</strong>. Now let’s see which icons are already available from Font Awesome 5.x as embedded into the Butterfly theme. </p>
<h3 id="By-fas-prefix"><a href="#By-fas-prefix" class="headerlink" title="By fas prefix"></a>By <code>fas</code> prefix</h3><p>Use examples are as follows:<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-user&quot;&gt; fa-user&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-video&quot;&gt; fa-video&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-folder&quot;&gt; fa-folder&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-image&quot;&gt; fa-image&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-heart&quot;&gt; fa-heart&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-bars&quot;&gt; fa-bars&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>This is how they look like:<br><i class="fas fa-user"> fa-user</i><br><i class="fas fa-video"> fa-video</i><br><i class="fas fa-folder"> fa-folder</i><br><i class="fas fa-image"> fa-image</i><br><i class="fas fa-heart"> fa-heart</i><br><i class="fas fa-bars"> fa-bars</i></p>
<h3 id="By-fab-prefix"><a href="#By-fab-prefix" class="headerlink" title="By fab prefix"></a>By <code>fab</code> prefix</h3><p>Use examples are as follows:<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fab fa-android&quot;&gt; fa-android&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fab fa-apple&quot;&gt; fa-apple&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;	</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fab fa-bluetooth&quot;&gt; fa-bluetooth&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;	</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fab fa-bluetooth-b&quot;&gt; fa-bluetooth-b&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fab fa-alipay&quot;&gt; fa-alipay&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;	</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fab fa-qq&quot;&gt; fa-qq&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>This is how they look like:<br><i class="fab fa-android"> fa-android</i><br><i class="fab fa-apple"> fa-apple</i><br><i class="fab fa-bluetooth"> fa-bluetooth</i><br><i class="fab fa-bluetooth-b"> fa-bluetooth-b</i><br><i class="fab fa-alipay"> fa-alipay</i><br><i class="fab fa-qq"> fa-qq</i></p>
<h3 id="The-Icon-Cheatsheet"><a href="#The-Icon-Cheatsheet" class="headerlink" title="The Icon Cheatsheet"></a>The Icon Cheatsheet</h3><p>Here is an exhaustive list of all icons that are available from Font Awesome 5.x, and you will need to search first before you could pick the desired proper ones for free adoption into your own project. </p>
<p><a href="https://www.fontawesomecheatsheet.com/font-awesome-cheatsheet-5x/">Font Awesome Cheatsheet v5.x</a></p>
<h2 id="Icons-for-Audio-Video"><a href="#Icons-for-Audio-Video" class="headerlink" title="Icons for Audio / Video"></a>Icons for Audio / Video</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-power-off&quot;&gt; fa-power-off&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-play&quot;&gt; fa-play&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; 	&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-play-circle&quot;&gt;fa-play-circle&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-pause&quot;&gt; fa-pause&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; 	&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-pause-circle&quot;&gt; fa-pause-circle&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-stop&quot;&gt; fa-stop&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; 	&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-stop-circle&quot;&gt; fa-stop-circle&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-step-backward&quot;&gt; fa-step-backward&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; 	&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-step-forward&quot;&gt; fa-step-forward&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; </span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-fast-backward&quot;&gt; fa-fast-backward&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; 	&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-fast-forward&quot;&gt; fa-fast-forward&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; </span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-signal&quot;&gt; fa-signal&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fab fa-bluetooth&quot;&gt; fa-bluetooth&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; 	&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fab fa-bluetooth-b&quot;&gt; fa-bluetooth-b&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-bell&quot;&gt; fa-bell&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; 	&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-bell-slash&quot;&gt; fa-bell-slash&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; </span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-headphones&quot;&gt; fa-headphones&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; 	&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-headphones-alt&quot;&gt; fa-headphones-alt&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; 	&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-headset&quot;&gt; fa-headset&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-microphone&quot;&gt; fa-microphone&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; 	&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-microphone-slash&quot;&gt; fa-microphone-slash&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-microphone-alt&quot;&gt; fa-microphone-alt&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; 	&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-microphone-alt-slash&quot;&gt; fa-microphone-alt-slash&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;	</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-music&quot;&gt; fa-music&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-volume-down&quot;&gt; fa-volume-down&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; 	&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-volume-up&quot;&gt; fa-volume-up&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-volume-off&quot;&gt; fa-volume-off&lt;&#x2F;i&gt; 		&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fas fa-volume-mute&quot;&gt; fa-volume-mute&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><i class="fas fa-power-off"> fa-power-off</i><br><i class="fas fa-play"> fa-play</i>     <i class="fas fa-play-circle">fa-play-circle</i><br><i class="fas fa-pause"> fa-pause</i>     <i class="fas fa-pause-circle"> fa-pause-circle</i><br><i class="fas fa-stop"> fa-stop</i>     <i class="fas fa-stop-circle"> fa-stop-circle</i><br><i class="fas fa-step-backward"> fa-step-backward</i>     <i class="fas fa-step-forward"> fa-step-forward</i><br><i class="fas fa-fast-backward"> fa-fast-backward</i>     <i class="fas fa-fast-forward"> fa-fast-forward</i><br><i class="fas fa-signal"> fa-signal</i><br><i class="fab fa-bluetooth"> fa-bluetooth</i>     <i class="fab fa-bluetooth-b"> fa-bluetooth-b</i><br><i class="fas fa-bell"> fa-bell</i>     <i class="fas fa-bell-slash"> fa-bell-slash</i><br><i class="fas fa-headphones"> fa-headphones</i>     <i class="fas fa-headphones-alt"> fa-headphones-alt</i>     <i class="fas fa-headset"> fa-headset</i><br><i class="fas fa-microphone"> fa-microphone</i>     <i class="fas fa-microphone-slash"> fa-microphone-slash</i><br><i class="fas fa-microphone-alt"> fa-microphone-alt</i>     <i class="fas fa-microphone-alt-slash"> fa-microphone-alt-slash</i><br><i class="fas fa-music"> fa-music</i><br><i class="fas fa-volume-down"> fa-volume-down</i>     <i class="fas fa-volume-up"> fa-volume-up</i><br><i class="fas fa-volume-off"> fa-volume-off</i>         <i class="fas fa-volume-mute"> fa-volume-mute</i></p>
